## 1. Package Version Changes

| Package | PF5 Version | PF6 Version | Notes |
|---------|------------|------------|-------|
| `@patternfly/react-core` | ^5.x | ^6.x (latest 6.5.1) | Major version bump |
| `@patternfly/react-table` | ^5.x | ^6.x (latest 6.5.1) | Major version bump |
| `@patternfly/react-icons` | ^5.x | ^6.x (latest 6.5.1) | Major version bump |
| `@patternfly/react-charts` | ^7.x | ^8.x (latest 8.5.1) | Major version bump; Victory is now optional peer dep |
| `@patternfly/react-tokens` | ^5.x | ^6.x (latest 6.5.1) | Token naming completely overhauled |
| `@patternfly/react-styles` | ^5.x | ^6.x (latest 6.5.1) | Major version bump |
| `@patternfly/pf-codemods` | N/A | `@latest` | Run with `--v6` flag |
| `victory` (peer dep) | bundled | optional peer dep | Must install separately if using charts |

### Action Items:
- [ ] Update all `@patternfly/*` packages to v6 in `package.json`
- [ ] Update `@patternfly/react-charts` to v8
- [ ] If using charts, install `victory` as a direct dependency (or specific packages like `victory-core`, `victory-tooltip`)
- [ ] Run `npm install` / `yarn install` to resolve all peer dependency warnings

---

## 2. Codemod Tools

PatternFly provides **4 codemod tools**. Run them in this order:

### 2a. Main Codemods (`pf-codemods`)
```bash
# Step 1: Dry run (see what would change)
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6

# Step 2: Apply fixes
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --fix
```
**Handles:** Component prop renames/removals, import path updates, component renames, enum renames
**Does NOT handle:** CSS variable updates, class name updates, some EmptyState refactoring, color token replacements (marks them with hot pink placeholder)

### 2b. Class Name Updater
```bash
npx @patternfly/class-name-updater <path> --v6 --fix
```
**Handles:** Replacing `pf-v5` CSS class prefixes with `pf-v6`

### 2c. Tokens Update (part of pf-codemods)
**Handles:** Global non-color CSS variables → auto-fix; Global color tokens → replaced with `t_temp_dev_tbd` / `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink, **must be manually replaced**)
**Does NOT handle:** Component-level tokens (`c_*`), chart tokens — these need manual replacement

### 2d. CSS Vars Updater
```bash
npx @patternfly/css-vars-updater <path>
```
**Handles:** CSS variable updates in non-React files (`.css`, `.scss`, `.md`, etc.)

### Action Items:
- [ ] Run main codemods (`--v6`) first, before any manual changes
- [ ] Run with `--fix` flag after reviewing dry-run output
- [ ] Run codemods **multiple times** until no more changes
- [ ] Run `class-name-updater --v6 --fix`
- [ ] Run `tokens-update` for React token updates
- [ ] Run `css-vars-updater` for `.css`/`.scss` files
- [ ] Search codebase for `t_temp_dev_tbd` and `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` — manually replace each with correct PF6 token
- [ ] Search for any remaining `--pf-v5-` prefixes and update manually

---

## 3. Component Removals & Deprecations

### Fully Removed (no PF6 equivalent — must rewrite):
| Removed Component | Replacement |
|---|---|
| `ApplicationLauncher` | Custom menu with `Menu`/`MenuToggle`/`Popper` |
| `ContextSelector` | Custom menu with `Menu`/`MenuToggle`/`Popper` |
| `Dropdown` (deprecated/old) | Current composable `Dropdown` or `DropdownTemplate` |
| `OptionsMenu` | Composable `Select` or `SelectTemplate` |
| `PageHeader` | `Masthead` + `Toolbar` |
| `Select` (deprecated/old) | Current composable `Select` or `SelectTemplate` |
| `KebabToggle` | `MenuToggle variant="plain"` with `EllipsisVIcon` |
| `PageNavigation` | Removed entirely; use `PageSection` with nav |

### Deprecated (moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`):
| Component | Recommended Replacement |
|---|---|
| `Chip` / `ChipGroup` | `Label` / `LabelGroup` (with `variant="outline"`) |
| `Tile` | `Card` (new tile-like Card example) |
| `Modal` (old implementation) | New `Modal` (promoted from `/next`) |
| `DualListSelector` (old) | New `DualListSelector` (promoted from `/next`) |
| `DragDrop` | New `DragDrop` implementation |

### Renamed Components:
| Old Name | New Name |
|---|---|
| `Text` | `Content` |
| `TextContent` | `Content` |
| `TextList` | `Content component="ul"` or `Content component="ol"` |
| `TextListItem` | `Content component="li"` |
