## 4. Component API Changes

### Accordion
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `AccordionContent` | `isHidden` prop **removed** (auto-set by `isExpanded` on `AccordionItem`) |
| `AccordionToggle` | `isExpanded` prop **moved to** `AccordionItem` |
| `AccordionItem` | New wrapper renders a `div` element |

### Alert
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| Markup | Internal markup changes — check snapshot tests |

### Avatar
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `border` prop | **Removed** → use `isBordered` instead |

### Banner
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `variant` prop | **Removed** → use `color` or `status` props instead |
| Color values | `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"` |

### Button
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `isActive` prop | **Renamed** to `isClicked` |
| Icons as children | Must use `icon` prop for plain variant buttons (children → `icon` prop) |
| `isDisabled` | Now sets `disabled` attr, NOT `aria-disabled` (unless `component` ≠ "button") |
| `aria-disabled` | Only renders when `true` (previously always rendered) |
| Text wrapping | Button text now wrapped in `<span class="pf-v6-c-button__text">` — affects `byText` queries |
| `variant="favorite"` | New variant supported |

### Card
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| **Removed props:** | `isSelectableRaised`, `isDisabledRaised`, `hasSelectableInput`, `selectableInputAriaLabel`, `onSelectableInputChange`, `isFlat`, `isRounded` |
| Clickable cards | `selectableActions.selectableActionId` and `selectableActions.name` no longer needed for clickable-only cards |

### Checkbox / Radio
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `isLabelBeforeButton` prop | **Replaced** with `labelPosition="start"` |

### Drawer
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `DrawerHead` | `hasNoPadding` prop **removed**; `DrawerPanelBody` no longer rendered internally |
| `DrawerContent` | `colorVariant="no-background"` **removed**; new `"primary"` value added |
| `DrawerContent/PanelContent/Section` | `colorVariant="light-200"` → `colorVariant="secondary"` |
| `DrawerColorVariant` | `light200` → `secondary` |

### Empty State — ⚠️ MAJOR REFACTOR (see Section 5)

### ExpandableSection
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `isActive` prop | **Removed** |

### FormGroup
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `labelIcon` prop | **Renamed** (check codemod output) |
| `FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` | **Renamed** interface |

### HelperTextItem
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `hasIcon` prop | **Removed** (icon auto-renders when `variant` ≠ "default") |
| `isDynamic` prop | **Removed** |
| `screenReaderText` | Now renders only when `variant` ≠ "default" |

### JumpLinksItem
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `href` prop | Now **required** |
| Internal markup | Uses `Button` component internally |

### Label
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `isOverflowLabel` prop | **Replaced** with `variant="overflow"` |
| Color values | `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"` |

### LoginMainFooterLinksItem
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| Structure | Completely changed — pass everything as children directly |

### Masthead — ⚠️ SIGNIFICANT RESTRUCTURE
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `MastheadBrand` | **Renamed** to `MastheadLogo` |
| New `MastheadBrand` | New wrapper component |
| `backgroundColor` prop | **Removed** (theming not handled React-side) |
| Structure | `MastheadToggle` and `MastheadBrand`/`MastheadLogo` must be inside `MastheadMain` |

### MenuToggle
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `splitButtonOptions` prop | **Replaced** with `splitButtonItems` |
| `SplitButtonOptions` interface | **Deleted** |

### Nav
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `variant="tertiary"` | **Removed** → use `variant="horizontal-subnav"` |
| `theme` prop | **Removed** (theming not handled React-side) |
| `NavItem` | `hasNavLinkWrapper` prop **removed**; use `icon` prop for icons |

### Page
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `header` prop | **Renamed** to `masthead` |
| `tertiaryNav` prop | **Renamed** to `horizontalSubnav` |
| `isTertiaryNavGrouped` | **Renamed** to `isHorizontalSubnavGrouped` |
| `isTertiaryNavWidthLimited` | **Renamed** to `isHorizontalSubnavWidthLimited` |
| `PageNavigation` | **Removed** entirely |
| `PageSection` `variant` | Only accepts `"default"` or `"secondary"` (dark, light, etc. removed) |
| `PageSection` `type="nav"` | **Removed** |
| `PageSection` / `PageBreadcrumb` | `isWidthLimited` no longer controls body wrapper; use new `hasBodyWrapper` prop |
| `PageSidebar` | `theme` prop **removed** |
| `PageHeaderToolsItem` | `isSelected` prop **removed** |
| `PageToggleButton` | Replace `BarsIcon` child with `isHamburgerButton` prop |

### Pagination
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| Markup | Changed — check snapshot tests |

### Popper
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `appendTo` default | Updated (check components using Popper) |

### Switch
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `labelOff` prop | **Removed** (label should not change with on/off state) |

### Tabs
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `isSecondary` prop | **Renamed** (check codemod) |
| `variant="light300"` | **Removed** |
| Markup | Updated |

### DataListAction
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `isPlainButtonAction` prop | **Removed** |

