## 5. Significantly Refactored Components

### EmptyState ⚠️
**This is the biggest single component change. Codemods handle some but NOT all cases.**

| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| `EmptyStateHeader` | **No longer a separate component** — absorbed into `EmptyState` |
| `EmptyStateIcon` | **No longer a separate component** — absorbed into `EmptyState` |
| `EmptyState` `titleText` prop | New prop — replaces `EmptyStateHeader titleText` |
| `EmptyState` `headingLevel` prop | New prop — replaces `EmptyStateHeader headingLevel` |
| `EmptyState` `icon` prop | New prop — pass icon component directly (e.g., `icon={CubesIcon}`) |
| `EmptyState` `headerClassName` | New prop — replaces `EmptyStateHeader className` |
| Exports | `EmptyStateHeader` and `EmptyStateIcon` are **no longer exported** |

**Before (PF5):**
```jsx
<EmptyState>
  <EmptyStateHeader
    titleText="No results"
    headingLevel="h4"
    icon={<EmptyStateIcon icon={SearchIcon} />}
  />
  <EmptyStateBody>Body text</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>
```

**After (PF6):**
```jsx
<EmptyState titleText="No results" headingLevel="h4" icon={SearchIcon}>
  <EmptyStateBody>Body text</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>
```

### Modal ⚠️
The old `Modal` is deprecated → moved to `/deprecated`. The "next" `Modal` is now promoted.

| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| Old `Modal` import | Moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| New `Modal` (was in `/next`) | Now imported from `@patternfly/react-core` |
| API | New Modal has different composition-based API |

### DualListSelector ⚠️
| Change | Details |
|---|---|
| Old implementation | Moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| New implementation (was in `/next`) | Now imported from `@patternfly/react-core` |

### Text → Content ⚠️
| Old Component | New Equivalent |
|---|---|
| `<Text>` | `<Content component="p">` |
| `<Text component="h3">` | `<Content component="h3">` |
| `<TextContent>` | `<Content>` |
| `<TextList>` | `<Content component="ul">` |
| `<TextList component="ol">` | `<Content component="ol">` |
| `<TextListItem>` | `<Content component="li">` |
| `TextVariants` enum | `ContentVariants` enum |
| `TextProps` type | `ContentProps` type |
| `TextListVariants` | `ContentVariants` |
| `TextListItemVariants` | `ContentVariants` |
| `isVisited` prop | `isVisitedLink` prop |
| `isPlain` prop (TextList) | `isPlainList` prop |

### Masthead ⚠️
Significant structural change — see Section 4 above.

