## 7. CSS Variable/Token Changes

### Token Naming Convention Change
| PF5 Pattern | PF6 Pattern |
|---|---|
| `--pf-v5-global--*` | `--pf-t--global--*` |
| `--pf-v5-c-*` | `--pf-v6-c-*` |
| `--pf-v5-l-*` | `--pf-v6-l-*` |

### React Token Naming Convention Change
| PF5 Pattern | PF6 Pattern |
|---|---|
| `global_FontSize_lg` | `t_global_font_size_lg` |
| `global_Color_100` | `t_temp_dev_tbd` (must find correct replacement) |
| `global_BorderWidth_lg` | `global_border_width_extra_strong` |
| `global_FontWeight_normal` | `global_font_weight_body_default` |
| `global_link_Color_hover` | Must manually find PF6 equivalent |
| Token prefix for design tokens | All prefixed with `t_` |

### Key Token Replacements (examples)
| PF5 CSS Variable | PF6 CSS Variable |
|---|---|
| `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` | `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg` |
| `--pf-v5-global--BorderWidth--lg` | `--pf-t--global--border--width--extra-strong` |
| `--pf-v5-global--BoxShadow--sm` | `--pf-t--global--box-shadow--sm` |
| `--pf-v5-global--spacer--3xl` | `--pf-t--global--spacer--3xl` |
| `--pf-v5-global--ZIndex--lg` | `--pf-t--global--z-index--lg` |
| `--pf-v5-global--Color--100` | **No 1:1 mapping** — must manually choose from semantic tokens |
| `--pf-v5-global--Color--200` | **No 1:1 mapping** — must manually choose |
| `--pf-v5-c-*` (component tokens) | **No 1:1 mapping** — must manually find replacement |

### What the codemod handles:
- ✅ Global non-color tokens (spacers, font sizes, border widths, box shadows, z-index)
- ⚠️ Global color tokens → replaced with `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink) — **MUST manually replace**
- ❌ Component-level tokens (`--pf-v5-c-*`) — **NOT handled**, must replace manually
- ❌ Chart tokens — **NOT handled**

### Resources:
- [Removed variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true)
- [Added variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true)
- [All PF6 tokens reference](https://www.patternfly.org/tokens/all-patternfly-tokens)

