## 10. Icon Changes

### Button Icon Pattern
```jsx
// OLD (PF5) - icons as children
<Button variant="plain"><TimesIcon /></Button>

// NEW (PF6) - icons via `icon` prop
<Button variant="plain" icon={<TimesIcon />} />
```

### PageToggleButton
```jsx
// OLD (PF5)
<PageToggleButton><BarsIcon /></PageToggleButton>

// NEW (PF6)  
<PageToggleButton isHamburgerButton />
```

### NavItem Icons
- Icons should now be passed via the `icon` prop on `NavItem` (not as children)

### KebabToggle → MenuToggle
```jsx
// OLD
<KebabToggle onToggle={() => {}} />

// NEW
<MenuToggle variant="plain" icon={<EllipsisVIcon aria-hidden="true" />} onClick={() => {}} />
```

