## Migration Order (Recommended)

1. **Pre-flight**: Ensure PF5 upgrade is complete (if coming from PF4)
2. **Update `package.json`**: Bump all `@patternfly/*` to v6, charts to v8, install `victory`
3. **Run main codemods**: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6 --fix`
4. **Run codemods again**: Repeat until clean
5. **Run class-name-updater**: `--v6 --fix`
6. **Run tokens-update**: Fix React token names
7. **Run css-vars-updater**: Fix CSS/SCSS variables
8. **Manual: Fix hot pink tokens**: Search for `t_temp_dev_tbd` / `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd`
9. **Manual: Fix component tokens**: Replace `--pf-v5-c-*` references
10. **Manual: Remove/rewrite removed components**: ApplicationLauncher, old Select, old Dropdown, etc.
11. **Manual: Fix EmptyState**: Verify all EmptyState instances are correct
12. **Manual: Fix Masthead structure**: Verify nesting
13. **Manual: Update chart imports**: Add `/victory` subpath
14. **Remove old CSS overrides**: Most won't work due to renamed variables
15. **Update tests**: Fix snapshots, button queries, class name assertions
16. **Build and verify**: Fix remaining TypeScript/build errors
17. **Visual review**: Check UI for hot pink indicators and layout issues

