    <h4>What changed</h4>
    <p>React 18 removed the implicit <code>children</code> prop from <code>React.FC</code> and <code>React.SFC</code> (the latter was also removed entirely). Components that accept children must now explicitly declare <code>children?: React.ReactNode</code> in their props. <code>React.ReactFragment</code> was also removed in favor of <code>React.ReactNode</code>.</p>

